WEBVTT


01:22:23.313 --> 01:22:24.648 line:85.83%,end
This is Eun Chang-su.

01:22:25.607 --> 01:22:27.776 line:85.83%,end
You know my daughter's
being held hostage, right?

01:22:29.152 --> 01:22:33.198 line:85.83%,end
Could you order your agents
to release my daughter right away?

01:22:34.908 --> 01:22:36.910 line:85.83%,end
Then meet our demand first.

01:22:37.661 --> 01:22:40.038 line:85.83%,end
Send us 300 million dollars in three days.

01:22:40.121 --> 01:22:41.247 line:85.83%,end
Pardon?

01:22:41.915 --> 01:22:44.709 line:85.83%,end
But you agreed to receive it
after the operation was over.

01:22:44.793 --> 01:22:47.087 line:85.83%,end
If you don't send it to us in three days,

01:22:47.504 --> 01:22:49.297 line:85.83%,end
all of the hostages will die.

01:22:49.381 --> 01:22:50.382 line:85.83%,end
What?

01:22:51.216 --> 01:22:52.509 line:85.83%,end
Are you kidding me?

01:22:52.592 --> 01:22:55.136 line:85.83%,end
Remember. You have three days.

01:22:59.432 --> 01:23:00.517 line:85.83%,end
Hello?

01:23:00.767 --> 01:23:01.601 line:85.83%,end
Hello?

01:23:51.443 --> 01:23:54.237 line:85.83%,end
KILL ALL HOSTAGES DAY BEFORE ELECTION

